Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.22,0:00:08.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,地の底の底の底
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.38,0:00:08.53,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,In the deep depths of the abyss!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.86,0:00:12.46,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,強制労働施設で開かれた\N地下チンチロ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.07,0:00:11.91,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Taking place in a slave labor facility, underground chinchiro!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.46,0:00:15.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,初めて親を受けたカイジを\N潰しにかかる
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.66,0:00:15.23,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,The foreman Ohtsuki and his underling Isawa
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.30,0:00:18.34,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,班長 大槻と 腹心 石和
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.59,0:00:17.92,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,seek to bankrupt Kaiji on his first deal!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.34,0:00:20.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,張りは それぞれ２万
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.64,0:00:20.22,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Each bets 20,000!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.57,0:00:23.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジ 大勝負！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.69,0:00:22.67,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Kaiji faces a fearsome foe!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.41,0:00:26.31,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,石和　シゴロ 倍づけ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.64,0:00:25.83,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Isawa rolls 4-5-6, which pays double!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.31,0:00:30.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,大槻　ゾロ目 ３倍づけ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.72,0:00:29.89,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,And Ohtsuki rolls triples, which pay triple!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.85,0:00:32.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,へたり込むカイジ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.01,0:00:35.51,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Kaiji sinks through the floor into debt hell!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.78,0:00:35.88,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,借金地獄突入
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.30,0:00:48.60,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,25日が過ぎた
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.40,0:00:48.13,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Twenty five days pass!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.11,0:01:04.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,はーい 皆の衆
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.32,0:01:04.12,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Okay, gentlemen!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.15,0:01:06.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お待ちかねの給料日です
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.48,0:01:06.42,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,It's finally payday!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.58,0:01:10.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,１ヵ月の勤労 ご苦労さま
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.85,0:01:09.73,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Thanks for your hard work this month!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.86,0:01:12.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,はい
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.96,0:01:12.36,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.79,0:01:17.20,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,月に１度 この先の見えぬ\N地下生活に訪れる
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.08,0:01:18.90,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Once a month, a brief glimpse of hope is offered to those trapped in this abyss.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.20,0:01:19.60,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ささやかな癒やし
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.29,0:01:19.73,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.60,0:01:23.47,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だがカイジにとっては\N思い知らされる日
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.73,0:01:22.88,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,But for Kaiji, this day instead offers him a lesson.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.47,0:01:26.97,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,現在 自分が置かれた境遇を
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.79,0:01:26.44,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,It informs him of his folly!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.04,0:01:33.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,はーい それでは\Nお待たせしました
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.26,0:01:33.70,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Oh, and sorry to keep you waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.81,0:01:36.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,４５組の皆さーん
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.03,0:01:35.68,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,It's time for the 45s!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.52,0:01:46.99,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジを含めた この６人の男たち
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.79,0:01:46.10,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Six men, including Kaiji.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.99,0:01:50.90,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,はい 北川さん　お疲れさま
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.25,0:01:49.87,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Here, Kitagawa. Good work this month.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.90,0:01:54.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,受け取る給料は２ヵ月先の前借り
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.20,0:01:54.14,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,The pay he receives now is an advance on two months hence!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.57,0:01:58.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そこから班長の手数料を\N引かれた金額
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.64,0:01:57.99,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,From it is removed the foreman's share!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.24,0:02:02.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,つまり正規の金額９万1000の\N半分以下
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.52,0:02:02.20,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Thus, it is less than half his true salary!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.91,0:02:05.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,４万5000ペリカ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.09,0:02:04.75,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Only 45,000 perica!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.78,0:02:10.31,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いずれもカイジと同じ\N博打で借金地獄に落ち
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.00,0:02:13.14,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,These men, like Kaiji, have been condemned by their gambling losses to debt hell!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.31,0:02:13.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,４万5000しか受け取れぬ男たち
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.89,0:02:19.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジを含めたこの６人は\N侮蔑を込めて こう呼ばれていた
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.10,0:02:18.46,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,These six are mocked as such:
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.12,0:02:21.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,４５組！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.39,0:02:20.90,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,The 45s!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.13,0:02:24.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お疲れさま カイジ君
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.44,0:02:23.64,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Good work, Kaiji.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.73,0:02:27.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あれ？どうしたのかな
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.86,0:02:27.02,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.63,0:02:30.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,君も前借りが必要だろう？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.01,0:02:30.07,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,You need an advance, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.57,0:02:34.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,クソッ この給料を叩き返し
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.86,0:02:31.62,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Dammit...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.51,0:02:36.64,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,If I hand this right back and don't take next month's pay...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.41,0:02:38.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,来月の給料をもらわなければ\N借金はチャラ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.78,0:02:38.05,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I'm out of the hole.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.41,0:02:41.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,２ヵ月 耐えれば… 耐えれば…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.72,0:02:41.21,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,If I can just hold on for two months...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.05,0:02:50.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,はい！ビール冷えてるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.45,0:02:48.36,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Cold beer, right here!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.42,0:02:52.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,5000ペリカ 5000ペリカ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.59,0:02:52.59,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Only 5,000 perica!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.89,0:02:55.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,キンキンに冷えてるよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.99,0:02:54.93,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,It's ice-cold!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.36,0:02:59.90,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,２ヵ月 耐え忍ぶ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.55,0:02:59.10,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,To endure two months!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.90,0:03:03.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今のカイジに\Nそんな気力は残っていない
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.14,0:03:02.98,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Kaiji no longer has such willpower!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.31,0:03:10.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もう届かない
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.55,0:03:09.70,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,It is unreachable!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.24,0:03:13.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,遠のいてしまった希望
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.45,0:03:12.94,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,His hopes recede!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.64,0:03:16.21,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,１日外出券！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.83,0:03:15.63,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,His hopes of the one-day furlough!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.21,0:03:20.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,別にいいさ\Nもともと無理だったんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.35,0:03:17.42,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,It doesn't matter anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.38,0:03:21.76,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I never could've saved up half a million anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.15,0:03:23.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,50万ためるなんて
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.79,0:03:28.23,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,大体 あの外出券には\Nただし書きがある
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.95,0:03:26.61,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Plus, there's a catch to the furlough anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.23,0:03:32.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,組織が適正と判断した場合に限る
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.44,0:03:31.51,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Only those approved by management are permitted a furlough!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.56,0:03:37.17,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,入って間もない俺を\N上があっさり認めるわけがねえ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.75,0:03:36.33,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I just got here. They'd never let me back out so soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.17,0:03:39.17,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どうせ無理
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.30,0:03:38.16,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,It's no good.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.47,0:03:43.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それに外に出れたって
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.70,0:03:48.05,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Even if I make it out, I'd never be able to bay back ten million in a day.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.87,0:03:49.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,1000万なんて金\N１日でなんとかなるわけがねえ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.08,0:03:54.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,己の心の弱さ 現実から目を背け\N言い聞かせる
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.29,0:03:53.90,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Kaiji, hiding from the truth of his weakness, makes excuses!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.85,0:03:59.99,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もともと絵空事\Nあり得ない夢　幻
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.04,0:03:58.42,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,It was always nothing but an impossible dream!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.55,0:03:59.56,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,A phantasm!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.99,0:04:03.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,決して かなわぬ幻
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.20,0:04:02.72,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,An unattainable phantasm!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.19,0:04:07.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,結局 俺は働くしかねえんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.37,0:04:06.01,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I've just gotta keep working.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.06,0:04:09.93,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この地獄で15年
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.34,0:04:08.99,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Fifteen years in this hell...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.93,0:04:12.60,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,クソッ… あ？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.05,0:04:10.54,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.24,0:04:20.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どうした？おい
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.44,0:04:17.94,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,What's wrong!?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.07,0:04:21.09,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Hey, are you okay!?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.14,0:04:22.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,大丈夫か？\Nどうした？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.09,0:04:21.87,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.48,0:04:26.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ダメだ こりゃ\N前田　病棟へ運んでやれ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.65,0:04:23.59,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Merde.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.92,0:04:25.94,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Maeda! Take him to the clinic!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.18,0:04:29.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,はい 分かりました\Nカイジ君　手伝ってくれ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.45,0:04:27.32,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.83,0:04:28.84,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Give me a hand, Kaiji.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.05,0:04:31.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,え？ああ…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.72,0:04:37.46,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,大丈夫だ…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.87,0:04:34.55,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I'm fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.46,0:04:41.27,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,大丈夫だよ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.57,0:04:38.39,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Wait! I'm fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.27,0:04:43.33,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,働ける…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.46,0:04:42.19,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I can work!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.33,0:04:45.33,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まだ働ける！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.66,0:04:44.85,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I can still work!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.94,0:04:54.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,初めてだ　こっちのエリアは
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.25,0:04:53.23,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,This is the first time I've been in this area.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.85,0:04:58.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,やだ… あそこは
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.20,0:04:55.61,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.34,0:04:57.13,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Not there!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.38,0:05:02.29,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,頼む！あそこは いやだ！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.55,0:05:00.87,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Please! Anywhere but there!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.29,0:05:05.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まだ働ける　まだ働ける…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.55,0:05:03.55,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I can still work!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.70,0:05:05.49,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I can still...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.79,0:05:08.29,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,先生　急患です
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.89,0:05:07.44,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Doc! Another emergency!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.37,0:05:23.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そこに広がるのは地獄の中の地獄
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.44,0:05:22.24,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,What lay before him was a hell within a hell!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.11,0:05:25.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,行き止まりの光景
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.38,0:05:24.84,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,The end of the line!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.51,0:05:30.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,粉塵に肺をやられ\N体を壊した者たち
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.71,0:05:29.00,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Men whose strenuous labor had destroyed their bodies!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.15,0:05:32.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,負け組の末路！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.28,0:05:32.11,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Those abandoned to their fate!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.75,0:05:35.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,先生
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.93,0:05:33.48,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Doc!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.02,0:05:37.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ああ その辺に置いといて
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.36,0:05:37.10,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Yeah, sure, leave 'im over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.59,0:05:41.29,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あとで寝床 作っておくから\Nあ はい
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.74,0:05:39.75,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I'll find him a mat later.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.35,0:05:41.03,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.53,0:05:46.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なんか まともな治療\N受けてるようには
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.78,0:05:48.19,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,It doesn't seem like they're going to take very good care of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.83,0:05:48.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,見えなかったけど
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.77,0:05:50.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,薬は高いからな
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.01,0:05:50.58,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Meds are expensive.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.74,0:05:54.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,高いって… 金が要るのか？\N当たり前だ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.11,0:05:51.95,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Expensive!?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.39,0:05:53.23,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,You have to pay?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.82,0:05:54.69,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.64,0:05:59.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,持ってるわけないだろ\N体を壊しちまったら 金なんて
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.10,0:05:56.29,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,But there's no way he can afford it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.81,0:05:58.95,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,If he's that beat up, he could never earn enough...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.78,0:06:03.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だから７～８割 戻らない\Nえ？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.92,0:06:01.98,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,That's why about three quarters of the men who go there never come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.58,0:06:07.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,一度 体を壊したら\Nおしまいなんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.69,0:06:05.25,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Once you break down...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.94,0:06:08.17,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,It's the end for men like us.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.25,0:06:09.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺たちは
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.76,0:06:22.47,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,冗談じゃねえ… 冗談じゃねえ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.94,0:06:18.07,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,That's bullshit!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.95,0:06:21.14,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,That's total bullshit!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.47,0:06:24.47,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,冗談じゃねえ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.65,0:06:23.74,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,That's complete and total bullshit!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.04,0:06:29.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,耐えてみせる
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.23,0:06:28.05,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I'll endure.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.41,0:06:32.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,50万をためるまで
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.61,0:06:30.97,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Until I've got my half-million.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.08,0:06:36.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,欲望を断ち切って 外へ出るんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.21,0:06:35.72,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I'll hold back my desires, and make it out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.78,0:06:42.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だが わずか１週間で揺らぐ決意
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.04,0:06:42.00,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,But in only a week, his resolve crumbles!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.65,0:06:47.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,代わりに頭をもたげてくる\N発散の欲望
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.88,0:06:46.21,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Instead, his mind is filled with desire!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.16,0:06:49.26,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,快楽の考思
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.36,0:06:49.04,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,And during recreation!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.03,0:06:55.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,クソッ もうなんでもいい！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.30,0:06:55.41,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Dammit! I don't care anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.77,0:06:59.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ダイブしたい　欲望の海に！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.88,0:06:58.70,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,He wants to dive into a sea of desire!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.00,0:07:00.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,崩れ落ちたい…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.21,0:07:00.21,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I want to collapse!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.91,0:07:03.37,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Abandon himself to utter destruction!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.94,0:07:05.21,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,身を委ねたい　破滅に！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.21,0:07:08.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,頑張りましょう\Nここで使っちゃダメだ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.53,0:07:08.13,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Keep trying! You can't spend it here!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.48,0:07:10.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あと数時間でしょ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.68,0:07:09.88,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Remember, there's only a few more hours!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.41,0:07:12.35,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あと数時間？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.66,0:07:11.81,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,A few days?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.35,0:07:15.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺もカイジさんと同じ気持ちです
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.40,0:07:14.78,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I feel the same way as you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.25,0:07:18.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なんのことだ？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.51,0:07:16.42,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.16,0:07:21.99,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,悲願は１日外出券　ですよね？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.44,0:07:20.19,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,All we want is the one-day furlough!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.05,0:07:21.73,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Am I right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.99,0:07:23.93,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ああ　まあな
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.82,0:07:23.46,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.93,0:07:27.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それを今夜 大勝ちして\Nゲットしようっていうんでしょ？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.03,0:07:27.54,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,So if we win big tonight, we'll be able to get our hands on it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.80,0:07:29.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,大勝ち？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.13,0:07:28.55,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Win big?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.55,0:07:30.92,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,At chinchiro!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.73,0:07:32.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,チンチロですよ\Nは？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.24,0:07:34.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この三好という男
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.53,0:07:37.49,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,This man, Miyoshi, heedless of Kaiji's failure,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.71,0:07:37.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あのカイジの ありさまを\N見ていたにもかかわらず
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.71,0:07:41.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,初日 自分が勝ったことで\N気をよくして
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.00,0:07:40.93,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,was emboldened by his first night's success
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.45,0:07:44.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,その後も毎回 賭場に参加
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.62,0:07:43.91,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,and participated in every session thereafter!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.18,0:07:46.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,気がつけば 前借り生活
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.36,0:07:46.09,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Before he realized it, he too was reduced to living on advances!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.55,0:07:50.32,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジと同じ ４５組に落ちたクチ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.73,0:07:49.84,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,A 45, just like Kaiji!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.32,0:07:53.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今夜こそ 俺\Nいけると思うんです 絶対に
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.57,0:07:52.62,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I really think I can win tonight!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.12,0:07:53.72,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I know it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.36,0:07:55.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,救えない男
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.72,0:07:55.00,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,You're hopeless.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.59,0:07:59.20,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,気が弱いくせに\N博打好きで お調子者
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.70,0:07:58.63,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,You don't have the nerves of steel a gambler needs. You just get carried away.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.20,0:08:02.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,たまに勝つと有頂天になって\Nすぐに転落
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.35,0:08:02.50,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,You love it when you finally win, but then the tables turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.73,0:08:04.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,100パーセント\N人生を失敗するタイプだ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.00,0:08:05.15,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,You're the kind of guy who's guaranteed to be a failure at life.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.80,0:08:08.21,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,頑張りましょう カイジさん
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.15,0:08:07.00,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Let's do our best, Kaiji!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.21,0:08:10.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺は博打なんてしない\Nえ？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.43,0:08:09.80,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,No more gambling.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.98,0:08:14.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,地道に50万ためる\N何 言ってるんすか！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.12,0:08:12.63,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I'll earn my 500,000 honestly.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.21,0:08:14.54,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Seriously!?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.58,0:08:17.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,前借りしてる俺たちが\N50万ためようと思ったら
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.76,0:08:19.88,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Counting our advances, that'll take a whole eight months!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.48,0:08:20.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,８ヵ月ですよ　８ヵ月！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.08,0:08:22.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺たちには無理です
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.27,0:08:21.64,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,It's impossible for us!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.02,0:08:25.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なぜなら意思が弱いから
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.15,0:08:24.34,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,We're too weak-willed!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.52,0:08:29.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジさん 今 もう\N崩れそうだったじゃないですか
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.72,0:08:28.93,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,You were just about to give up, weren't you!?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.13,0:08:31.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まだ１週間なのに
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.31,0:08:30.68,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,With only a week left!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.13,0:08:35.97,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺たちが外出券を手にするには\N博打で勝つしかないんです
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.49,0:08:35.57,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Gambling's the only way we'll ever earn enough for the furlough!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.97,0:08:39.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だから特別に\Nいいこと教えてあげます
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.26,0:08:39.12,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Plus, I'll let you in on something!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.77,0:08:42.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,出目にも いくつか\N傾向があるんです
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.17,0:08:42.18,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,There are patterns in how the dice come up!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.61,0:08:47.44,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,三好は自分が参加した賭場\Nすべての出目を克明にメモ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.78,0:08:47.17,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Miyoshi took detailed notes on each of the dice rolls in his games!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.44,0:08:51.82,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そのデータを検討\N勝ちの傾向を探っていた
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.70,0:08:51.44,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,And within that data, he found a pattern to the winning rolls!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.82,0:08:55.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だが結果は大敗 連敗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.95,0:08:54.82,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,But when attempting to use it, he failed! He lost every time!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.62,0:08:59.82,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ってことは結局 出目のデータも\N無意味ってことじゃねえか
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.82,0:08:59.46,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,So doesn't that just mean the data's useless?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.82,0:09:02.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ほら ここを見ると分かります
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.97,0:09:01.94,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Wait, look at this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.49,0:09:05.33,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この｢ハ｣っていうのが\N班長なんですけど
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.66,0:09:04.95,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,This "F" mark is for the foreman.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.33,0:09:08.23,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いや 班長の目はいつも強くって
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.53,0:09:08.15,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,He always rolls well.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.23,0:09:13.10,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それでも穴が まったくないって\Nわけじゃないんですけどね
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.63,0:09:12.01,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,But not perfectly, you know? {dongs}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.10,0:09:16.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ほら こことか
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.39,0:09:14.53,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Look at this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.77,0:09:18.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ここなんかも…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.90,0:09:17.89,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,And over here--
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.00,0:09:20.36,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Hey, what are you doing!?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.71,0:09:22.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何するんですか！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.45,0:09:24.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,偶然か？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.65,0:09:23.42,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Is this just a coincidence?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.78,0:09:27.69,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,大槻がいい目を出す時は必ず
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.06,0:09:26.98,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Every time Ohtsuki rolls really well...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.69,0:09:31.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,両隣に石和と沼川がいる
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.85,0:09:30.04,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,He's between Isawa and Numakawa...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.19,0:09:35.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺が負けたあの晩も同じだった
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.46,0:09:33.96,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,It was the same way when I lost!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.03,0:09:37.26,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,待てよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.29,0:09:35.93,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.26,0:09:40.46,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジの脳裏を貫く疑念
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.39,0:09:39.59,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,A thought pierces Kaiji's mind!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.46,0:09:43.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,サイコロってのは立方体だから
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.65,0:09:43.19,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Dice are cubic!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.40,0:09:48.84,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,こう見えても こう見えても…\Nまさか！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.73,0:09:45.96,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,So matter which way you look at them...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.24,0:09:47.83,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Is that it!?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.84,0:09:52.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,疑念が確信に変わる！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.03,0:09:51.59,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,This thought grows into conviction!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.48,0:09:54.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,偶然なんかじゃねえ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.65,0:09:54.26,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,This is no coincidence!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.81,0:09:57.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,許せねえ！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.03,0:09:55.85,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I'll get him for this!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.11,0:09:59.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,クソッ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.31,0:09:57.77,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.15,0:10:01.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジさん
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.51,0:10:00.15,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Kaiji?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.56,0:10:14.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あの野郎…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.96,0:10:12.82,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,That asshole!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.30,0:10:16.60,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あの野郎！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.48,0:10:15.43,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,That fucking asshole!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.60,0:10:18.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,許せねえ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.71,0:10:17.85,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I'll fucking get him!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.54,0:10:20.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,許してたまるか！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.88,0:10:20.40,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,He'll pay!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.01,0:10:28.01,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そりゃ傑作だ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.25,0:10:27.44,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,It works great, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.48,0:10:36.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,殴ってどうなる…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.64,0:10:35.10,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,But if I smack him...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.79,0:10:41.26,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,殴りつけて 怒鳴り散らして\Nそんなんじゃ…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.05,0:10:38.55,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,If I smack him and start yelling...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.28,0:10:40.03,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.26,0:10:43.23,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何も変わらない
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.44,0:10:42.72,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,It won't change anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.23,0:10:45.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,変わらないんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.60,0:10:44.89,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Nothing will change!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.73,0:10:47.13,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.63,0:10:51.47,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,第１土曜日 大槻班
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.65,0:10:53.86,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,On the first Saturday of the month, Ohtsuki sets up!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.47,0:10:54.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,大盆 開帳！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.76,0:11:02.81,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Aww man...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.95,0:11:07.22,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,仮に あの野郎の仕掛けが\N俺の読みどおりだったとして
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.08,0:11:06.60,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,If his trick is what I think it is...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.22,0:11:09.92,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,現場を押さえたとしても
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.29,0:11:08.94,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Even if I stand up right now and try to press him on it...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.92,0:11:12.82,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,｢初めてだ　出来心だ｣とか言って
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.99,0:11:12.45,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,He'll say he's never done it before.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.82,0:11:16.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,せいぜい その勝負を\N倍払いで済ます
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.97,0:11:15.36,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,And at best he'll just pay double.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.19,0:11:19.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そんな世間ずれした\Nぬらりとした やり口で
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.28,0:11:20.80,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I can't settle for just that!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.13,0:11:21.53,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,くぐり抜けられてたまるか
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.53,0:11:25.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もっと致命的 壊滅的な打撃を！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.70,0:11:24.35,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I need to hit him harder! Wipe him out!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.10,0:11:29.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どうしたらいい？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.17,0:11:28.05,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,What do I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.51,0:11:32.21,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どうしたら…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.66,0:11:30.40,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,What do I do!?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.15,0:11:34.70,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Kaiji's thoughts meander...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.21,0:11:36.21,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,めまぐるしく回る思考
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.21,0:11:38.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そして 見える
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.42,0:11:37.39,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,And then!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.90,0:11:38.43,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,He sees!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.98,0:11:41.99,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,突破口！その糸口！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.07,0:11:40.08,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,An opening!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.50,0:11:41.64,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,That hint!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.22,0:11:50.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いける！これなら倒せる
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.39,0:11:47.80,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I can do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.52,0:11:51.25,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I can beat Ohtsuki with this!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.13,0:11:52.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,大槻を！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.43,0:11:56.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だが奴を完全にぶっ潰すには
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.43,0:11:57.23,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,But I can't completely wipe him out by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.07,0:11:58.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,一人じゃ無理
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.04,0:12:01.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,数だ　頭数が必要だ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.30,0:12:00.65,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Numbers! I need strength in numbers!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.27,0:12:07.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジが近づいたのは\N４５組の男たち
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.42,0:12:07.08,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Kaiji notices the 45s!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.68,0:12:13.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今宵も勝負に敗れ\Nスカンピン どん底の負け組
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.86,0:12:12.07,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Perpetual penniless losers!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.12,0:12:16.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,つくづく お前らって負け組だよな
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.28,0:12:15.52,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,You guys are total losers.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.02,0:12:19.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あ？\N鏡を見てみるといい
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.58,0:12:18.77,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Look in the mirror.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.96,0:12:23.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そろいもそろって\N典型的なダメ人間
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.26,0:12:21.64,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Each and every one of you are exactly what people think of
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.64,0:12:23.22,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,when they talk about the scum of society.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.76,0:12:27.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,クズでございってツラが\N映るからよう
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.91,0:12:26.25,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,And you just accept it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.50,0:12:30.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,一生 浮かび上がれねえ顔だ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.70,0:12:29.66,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,You'll never climb out of this pit.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.40,0:12:33.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いきなり なんだ てめえ？\Nカイジさん！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.83,0:12:32.08,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,What the fuck's your problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.50,0:12:33.33,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Kaiji!?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.30,0:12:37.47,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺もだ　俺も同じ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.44,0:12:34.04,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I know because I'm the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.23,0:12:36.14,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I'm the same way.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.47,0:12:40.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,気がつきゃ 人生の隅っこ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.51,0:12:40.07,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I've realized that the dim corners of life...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.71,0:12:42.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,世間の片隅
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.79,0:12:42.02,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,The back alleys of society...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.98,0:12:45.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そこが指定席
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.12,0:12:44.25,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Are our places.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.25,0:12:49.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,認められず 軽んじられ 疎まれ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.45,0:12:48.85,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Rejected, despised, shunned...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.85,0:12:51.97,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Unable to endure it, we fall further and further.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.09,0:12:52.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それに耐えられず 落下に次ぐ落下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.79,0:12:57.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,学校でも社会でも\N落ち続ける落下人生
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.94,0:12:56.87,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,In school, in society... Fall after fall.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.56,0:13:00.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,こんな地の底まで落ちて…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.63,0:12:59.34,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,All the way into this abyss.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.43,0:13:04.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なのに なんだ！\Nここでも また負け組か
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.61,0:13:03.68,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,And what!? Are we still going to be losers here!?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.70,0:13:08.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この地の果てで\Nまた負けるんかい！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.89,0:13:07.05,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Have we come all the way here to fail again!?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.91,0:13:13.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,仲間かと思った班長にも\N食い物にされてよ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.06,0:13:12.23,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Even the foreman acts friendly in order to use us.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.18,0:13:16.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,気がつきゃ給料の半分をピンハネ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.24,0:13:15.52,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Before we even noticed, he was taking half our salary.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.05,0:13:19.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なんだ これ？\Nマヌケもいいとこだぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.26,0:13:18.91,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Guess there is a use for idiots.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.55,0:13:23.32,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,その上 みんなも\N聞いたことあるだろうが
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.68,0:13:22.74,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Oh, and I'm sure you already know this...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.32,0:13:25.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,班長たちは\Nビールやつまみを売って
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.47,0:13:28.54,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,But the foreman and his gang split the beer and snacks money with Teiai.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.79,0:13:29.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,その利益を\N帝愛と折半してるらしい
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.19,0:13:32.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そいつに俺たちから\Nピンハネした金額を合わせると
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.32,0:13:32.15,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Add that up with the interest he's charging us,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.86,0:13:36.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,班長の懐に\N一体いくら入ると思う？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.00,0:13:35.56,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,and just how much money do you think he socks away?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.50,0:13:39.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ざっと計算して 72万だ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.66,0:13:39.31,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,If I had to guess, I'd say around 720,000.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.77,0:13:42.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,な… 70…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.75,0:13:41.53,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Seven hundred!?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.07,0:13:46.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何これ？コツコツ毎月９万ずつ\N半年以上ためるなんて
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.17,0:13:43.03,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.67,0:13:48.17,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,You think you can just save up half a million at 90 thou a month? That's retarded!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.91,0:13:49.21,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,バカ丸出しじゃねえか
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.21,0:13:52.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,大槻なら きっと\Nこう言うだろうぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.36,0:13:51.28,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Think what Ohtsuki would be saying!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.25,0:13:55.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,正気の沙汰じゃねえな
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.56,0:13:55.48,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Now that's silly, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.20,0:14:09.60,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,大槻たちが潤い続け\N俺たちがそれを支える
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.29,0:14:08.94,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Ohtsuki and his gang get fat off our backs!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.60,0:14:11.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それでいいのかよ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.81,0:14:10.94,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Are you okay with that!?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.54,0:14:13.47,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,仕方ねえだろ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.77,0:14:12.59,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,We're damned either way.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.42,0:14:16.64,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,It doesn't matter what you say, we can't do anything about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.47,0:14:16.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今さら そんなこと言ったって\Nどうにもなりゃしねえ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.94,0:14:20.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そうですよ カイジさん\N仕方ないじゃないですか
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.15,0:14:20.45,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Yeah, Kaiji! We're stuck!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.81,0:14:23.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いいのか？\Nこのまま負け組のままで
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.94,0:14:23.54,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Do you just want to keep being losers?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.71,0:14:25.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,僕は負け組じゃない！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.79,0:14:25.40,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I'm not a loser!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.65,0:14:27.92,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いや 負け組だ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.91,0:14:27.22,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Yeah you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.92,0:14:31.22,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,違う 違う 違う　聞きたくない！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.00,0:14:29.42,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,No, no, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.79,0:14:30.52,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I don't want to hear it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.22,0:14:34.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,みんな こんな奴 相手にするな
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.24,0:14:34.11,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Ignore him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.86,0:14:37.33,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,行こうぜ… あ？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.08,0:14:35.61,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Let's get out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.33,0:14:39.60,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,示す\N何？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.45,0:14:38.13,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I'll show you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.76,0:14:39.16,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.60,0:14:43.47,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺が勝ちへの道を示す\N道？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.80,0:14:42.00,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I'll show you how to win!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.55,0:14:43.24,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,How to win?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.47,0:14:47.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,班長を… 大槻を倒し 大金を得る
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.64,0:14:46.98,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,We can take down Ohtsuki, and then we'll be rich.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.70,0:14:49.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,勝つんだ　俺たちが！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.79,0:14:49.48,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,We can win!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.94,0:14:52.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,勝つって…\Nどうやって？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.03,0:14:51.13,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Win? You mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.59,0:14:52.28,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,How?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.58,0:14:56.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どうやって大金を？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.81,0:14:54.11,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,How do we win big?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.28,0:14:58.22,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,一度だけ奇跡を見せる
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.49,0:14:58.27,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I'll show you a miracle.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.22,0:15:00.22,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,奇跡？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.76,0:14:59.40,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,A miracle?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.22,0:15:03.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,大槻には\Nちょっとしたクセがあるのさ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.55,0:15:02.60,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Ohtsuki has this one little habit.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.75,0:15:07.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,場が沸騰して\Nまさに今ここぞって時に
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.87,0:15:08.93,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Right when the action gets hot--like right now--he has a habit of rolling well.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.09,0:15:09.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,勝負強くなるクセがな
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.49,0:15:12.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,勝負だ！\N俺も！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.66,0:15:10.25,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I'll take that bet!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.13,0:15:11.81,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Me too!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.06,0:15:14.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺もだ！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.08,0:15:12.90,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,And me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.47,0:15:20.10,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,頃合いだ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.60,0:15:17.46,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Just now...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.10,0:15:22.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いいか　一度だけだ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.26,0:15:22.18,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Just once...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.51,0:15:26.01,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ここ一度だけ\N班長の目を言い当てる
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.64,0:15:25.52,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Just this time, I'll guess the foreman's roll.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.01,0:15:28.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,え？\Nそんなこと できるわけ…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.93,0:15:28.47,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,That's impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.91,0:15:31.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,よーしと…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.48,0:15:31.00,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Here I go.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.18,0:15:33.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,目はシゴロだ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.36,0:15:33.09,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,It's gonna be 4-5-6.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.45,0:15:41.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,うっ…\Nなんじゃ これ！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.70,0:15:39.75,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,What!?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.02,0:15:43.26,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,悪いな 皆の衆
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.16,0:15:43.17,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Sorry, gentlemen.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.26,0:15:45.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,シゴロだ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.34,0:15:44.52,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,It's 4-5-6!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.73,0:15:48.60,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,当たった…\N当たった
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.85,0:15:46.72,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,You nailed it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.18,0:15:48.00,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,You were right...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.60,0:15:53.44,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,倍づけだ　怖いのう 博打は
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.72,0:15:49.64,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Looks like you're paying double.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.03,0:15:51.86,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Gambling really is fearsome.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.44,0:15:57.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ってことは イカサマか！野郎…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.59,0:15:55.97,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,He's cheating!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.51,0:15:57.46,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,That son of a bitch!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.11,0:16:00.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,待て！どうするつもりだ？\N決まってる！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.46,0:15:57.83,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.61,0:15:59.54,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,What are you gonna do?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.98,0:16:03.73,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Isn't it obvious? I'm gonna beat his ass until he owns up!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.91,0:16:03.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あいつをぶん殴ってでも\Nイカサマを白状させて…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.81,0:16:07.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それじゃダメだ　そんなことで\N済ましちゃダメなんだ！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.12,0:16:07.00,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,No! That won't solve anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.62,0:16:10.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だったら…\Nだったら どうする気だ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.77,0:16:10.52,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Then what? What do we do!?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.85,0:16:12.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いいから座れ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.97,0:16:12.05,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Sit back down!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.96,0:16:21.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,確かに奴の強運には\N偶然じゃない理由がある
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.09,0:16:20.67,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Yeah, his rolls aren't just luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.30,0:16:25.17,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だが それと同時に\N致命的な傷もある
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.44,0:16:24.51,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,But there's one fatal flaw.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.17,0:16:29.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そこを突く\Nただしチャンスは一度きりだ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.39,0:16:26.25,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,That's how we'll get him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.98,0:16:28.44,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,But we only have one chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.04,0:16:32.01,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,本当に一回こっきりだが
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.25,0:16:30.90,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,One single shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.01,0:16:35.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,奇襲で突き崩すことができる
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.23,0:16:34.14,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,We have to surprise him!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.41,0:16:38.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,散々 利用され続けてきた俺たちが
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.56,0:16:37.68,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,We've been used! Hoodwinked! Bamboozled!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.05,0:16:43.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,手にする千載一遇\N最初で最後のチャンス
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.12,0:16:41.65,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,This is our once-in-a-lifetime chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.42,0:16:46.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今ここで立たなかったら
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.51,0:16:45.19,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,If we don't stand up now...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.19,0:16:49.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺たちは生涯 奴隷だ！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.34,0:16:49.27,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,We'll be slaves for the rest of our lives!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.17,0:17:01.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,３万　俺の手持ち全額だ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.31,0:17:00.91,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I've got 30 thou.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.81,0:17:05.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,出してくれ\Nみんなも手持ちの金 全部
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.83,0:17:04.51,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Cough it up. Give me all your money.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.08,0:17:07.01,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,手持ち全部？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.15,0:17:06.89,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,All our money?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.01,0:17:10.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そうだ　どうせ\Nスッカラカン同然なんだろ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.25,0:17:10.14,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Yeah. We're all almost broke anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.73,0:17:11.42,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Hurry it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.75,0:17:12.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,早く
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.59,0:17:18.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,これだけだ　おい
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.78,0:17:16.75,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,This is all I have.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.48,0:17:18.03,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.49,0:17:20.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だ… 出しますよ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.58,0:17:20.17,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,What do I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.30,0:17:32.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,集まった金は 負け組\N４５組６人のなけなしの金
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.43,0:17:31.78,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,The losers, the 45s, gather what few pennies they have!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.50,0:17:35.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,わずかばかりの命の綱
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.70,0:17:34.93,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,The few threads holding them to life!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.41,0:17:38.01,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,５… ６… ７
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.53,0:17:37.55,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Five, six, seven...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.01,0:17:41.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,合計で６万2700
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.19,0:17:40.20,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,All together, we've got 62,700.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.78,0:17:45.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,これから３ヵ月 この金でしのぐ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.84,0:17:44.74,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,We endure for the next three months on this.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.48,0:17:47.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,しのぐ？\Nそうだ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.53,0:17:46.26,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Endure?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.48,0:17:48.82,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Yeah. We hold back on our meals.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.45,0:17:50.32,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,飲み食いは制限　酒は禁止
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.09,0:17:51.93,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,No drinking. One smoke a day.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.32,0:17:54.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,タバコは１日１本\N博打はもってのほかだ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.40,0:17:53.66,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,And absolutely no gambling.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.19,0:17:57.46,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ギリギリ切り詰めて 借金を返す
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.36,0:17:56.55,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,We live on the very edge, and pay off our loans.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.46,0:18:01.93,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,晴れて正規の給料９万を\N受け取れるようになったら
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.56,0:18:00.42,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,And once we start getting our 90 thou again...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.93,0:18:04.23,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,その金で
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.06,0:18:02.94,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,We take that money...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.23,0:18:07.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,大槻を殺る！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.26,0:18:05.54,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,And we take down Ohtsuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.00,0:18:09.27,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,小銭じゃ奴は殺せない
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.24,0:18:08.79,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,We need a bigger stack to finish him off.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.27,0:18:12.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,せいぜいビックリさせて終わりだ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.39,0:18:11.35,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,If he notices what's up, we're finished.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.08,0:18:15.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ダメなんだ そんなんじゃ\Nマックスでぶつかるんだ！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.17,0:18:13.42,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,We can't let that happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.96,0:18:15.15,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,We need to take him down in one shot! {take him down to the max. derp.}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.58,0:18:19.35,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今 俺たちがなし得る\N最高マックス！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.75,0:18:18.77,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Let's have one hell of a shot ready! {take him down to the ULTIMATE max. derrrp.}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.35,0:18:23.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,さあ もういい加減\N勝とうじゃないか！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.50,0:18:22.98,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,All right, let's win this one!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.85,0:18:27.22,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,重ねろ　この最初で最後の奇襲
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.89,0:18:24.82,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Give me your hands!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.41,0:18:28.91,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Everyone who's ready to stake everything on this surprise attack...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.22,0:18:29.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,最終戦略に乗る者は
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.59,0:18:32.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺の手に 手を！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.77,0:18:31.87,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Give me your hands!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.67,0:18:43.38,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Um... By 'winning big', you mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.67,0:18:43.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あの 大金ってことは つまり…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.61,0:18:46.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,外へ行ける金額ってこと？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.93,0:18:45.89,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,You mean getting enough money to get out of here?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.18,0:18:48.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,当然だ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.34,0:18:47.23,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.11,0:18:50.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そ… そうか
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.90,0:18:49.58,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.68,0:18:54.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,外へ… 外へ行けるなら…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.90,0:18:53.54,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,If... If this gets us out of here...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.77,0:18:55.46,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I'm in!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.89,0:18:56.82,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,乗った！\N他は？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.14,0:18:56.60,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,How about the rest of you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.82,0:18:59.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ああ… お 俺…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.35,0:19:01.04,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I... I only put in 1,300, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.16,0:19:02.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,1300しか出してねえんだけど\Nいいのか？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.37,0:19:01.96,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Am I okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.56,0:19:04.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そんなこと関係ねえ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.69,0:19:04.08,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,It doesn't matter how much you put in.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.49,0:19:08.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あの ワシ…\N今年42になるんだけど
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.71,0:19:08.60,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I... I'm turning 42 this year...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.50,0:19:10.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,関係ねえ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.79,0:19:09.87,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,That doesn't matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.63,0:19:14.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そ… それじゃ乗った\N乗った！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.93,0:19:12.43,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Then I'm in!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.97,0:19:13.37,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Me too!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.30,0:19:17.60,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お… 俺も乗せてくれ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.23,0:19:17.19,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Let me in too!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.35,0:19:24.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あと１人　どうする？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.41,0:19:24.33,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,One left. Are you in or out?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.25,0:19:30.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どうもこうもねえ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.44,0:19:28.67,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,There's no point in asking.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.15,0:19:32.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺は ぐうたらだ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.46,0:19:31.65,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I'm worthless.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.56,0:19:35.23,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ぐうたらで その日暮らし
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.59,0:19:38.09,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I don't do a damn thing with my life. {glossing stupid sfx word}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.23,0:19:38.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ダラダラ グズグズ生きてきた
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.80,0:19:43.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,でも本当は ずっと待ってた
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.86,0:19:43.76,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,But really I've always been waiting for this!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.03,0:19:46.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,こんな日を\Nなんとか立ち上がるきっかけを
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.57,0:19:51.63,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I was never able to stand up for myself alone, but now...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.50,0:19:52.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,一人じゃ どうしても\Nできなかったが 今度は…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.11,0:19:55.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,一緒に立ち上がりましょう\N前田さん！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.18,0:19:53.77,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,We stand together!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.47,0:19:55.11,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Maeda!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.98,0:19:58.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,立ち上がって 勝つんだ！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.19,0:19:58.48,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,We stand, and we win!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.75,0:20:06.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,４５組 結束！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.96,0:20:06.07,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,The 45s unite!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.49,0:20:09.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,負け犬集団の中の負け組
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.61,0:20:11.83,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Losers among losers, men trapped at the bottom of the abyss,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.19,0:20:15.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どん底の どん底男たちが\N今 その手を重ね 立ち上がる
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.22,0:20:14.91,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,they join hands and stand!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.75,0:20:18.25,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,To overthrow Ohtsuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.80,0:20:18.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,打倒 大槻！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.45,0:20:25.21,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Proverbs of Kaiji Returns!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.52,0:20:38.84,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,You're hopeless.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.85,0:20:43.56,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,You don't have the nerves of steel a gambler needs. You just get carried away.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.66,0:20:49.14,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,You love it when you finally win, but then the tables turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.82,0:20:56.20,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,You're the kind of guy who's guaranteed to be a failure at life.
